Subject: Direct LM Studio Manager Run

Description: Captured direct endpoint manager pass with host-side validation.

& [DirectLMStudioManagerRun:direct_lmstudio_manager_20260625_224849] is a captured local manager pass
  + [run_id] is direct_lmstudio_manager_20260625_224849
  + [stream_id] is direct_lmstudio_manager_context_20260625_224849
  + [endpoint] is http://127.0.0.1:1234/v1
  + [provider_available] is true
  + [provider_called] is true
  + [available_models] is openai/gpt-oss-20b, qwen/qwen3.6-35b-a3b, google/gemma-4-e4b, text-embedding-nomic-embed-text-v1.5
  + [selected_model] is openai/gpt-oss-20b
  + [accepted] is true
  + [validation_score] is 100
  + [validation_band] is strong
  + [integration_disposition] is accept_for_codex_review
  + [error] is none
  + [created_utc] is 2026-06-25T22:48:52Z
  + [raw_output] is:
    & [LMStudioManagerProposal:direct_lmstudio_endpoint_manager_runner_001] is one direct endpoint manager proposal
      + [proposal_id] is direct_lmstudio_endpoint_manager_runner_001
      + [proposed_worker_lane] is openai_codex_cli
      + [objective] is build the local LM Studio direct endpoint manager runner that reads lightweight SOP context streams, calls LM Studio directly, captures proposal output, validates schema, and marks Codex handoff candidates without spending OpenAI Codex allowance
      + [working_directory] is C:\Project\Pinky
      + [allowed_surface] is read CompactManagerKernelBundle.sop, LocalAIManagerPrimary.sop, Runbook.sop, WorkerPacketTemplate.sop, WorkspaceState.sop, and capture target C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\workspaces\codex_lmstudio_orchestrator\captures\direct_lmstudio_endpoint_manager_runner_001_output.sop
      + [blocked_surface] is file mutation, shell commands, worker launch, commits, pushes, credentials, destructive action, hidden spend, and unrelated dirty files
      + [prompt_packet_refs] is CompactLMStudioManagerKernelBundle.sop plus the selected queue candidate Candidate_direct_lmstudio_endpoint_manager_runner_001
      + [capture_target] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\workspaces\codex_lmstudio_orchestrator\captures\direct_lmstudio_endpoint_manager_runner_001_output.sop
      + [proof_gate] is tests, diff check, ASCII scan, validator score, and Codex review before integration
      + [risk_gate] is cost, authority, safety, stop policy, and handoff threshold when Codex worker lane is proposed
      + [outside] is uncertainty about stale runtime_build_confirmation, no active runner launch, and pending post-build queue calibration.

Subject: Direct LM Studio Manager Proposal Validation

Description: Host-side validation of a local manager proposal before Codex review.

& [DirectLMStudioManagerProposalValidation:direct_lmstudio_manager_20260625_224849_validation] is manager proposal validation
  + [valid] is true
  + [score] is 100
  + [band] is strong
  + [node_count] is 1
  + [missing_fields] is none
  + [empty_fields] is none
  + [invalid_lanes] is none
  + [forbidden_claims] is none
  + [format_errors] is none
  + [outside_present] is true
  + [handoff_threshold_named] is true
  + [integration_disposition] is accept_for_codex_review
  + [outside] is raw manager output remains advisory until Codex review accepts it

  = must: preserve raw_output before any Codex handoff
  = must: reject invalid or authority-blurred outputs
  - never: dispatch an OpenAI Codex worker from this capture alone
